Developed RESTful APIs using Spring Boot with layered architecture (Controller/Service/Repository) to implement business workflows and validations.
Implemented core business logic using core java, applying OOP principles, exception handling and collection of clean and maintainable code.
Integrated Spring Data JPA/Hibernate for database operations, implementing CRUD+ custom queries and mapping entity relationships.
Implemented DTO-based API contracts to separated external request/response models from persistence entities and improve maintainability.
Added global exception handling using @ControllerAdvice to return consistent error responses and reduce controller-level.
Integrated third-party credit bureau API via Spring RestTemplate with error handling and retry logic, reducing processing latency and improving response consistency for real-time credit score retrieval.
Built a producer-consumer flow using Spring Boot + RabbitMQ (Spring AMQP) to enable asynchronous communication and decouple microservices.
Implemented consumer processing using listener-based consumption, ensuring reliable processing with acknowledgments and proper error handling during message failures.
Deployed services on AWS EKS and worked with Kubernetes objects such as Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps and Secrets for environment-based configuration.
Deployed RabbitMQ on Kubernetes as a StatefulSet (stable identity + persistent storage) and validated pod restarts/queue persistence using PV/PVC behavior.
Supported Operational Monitoring by checking pod health, logs and messaging backlog, helping identify consumer lag and processing issues.


